Privacy Policy
CV Maker Resume Builder Privacy Policy
Introduction
Welcome to CV Maker App by App Resort ("we," "us," or "our"). This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our
CV Maker Resume Builder
(the "App").
By accessing or using the App, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with our practices, please do not use our App.
Information We Collect
We may collect and process the following types of personal information when you use our App:
2.1. Information You Provide:
Personal and contact information such as your name, email address, phone number, and postal address.
Information provided when you create or update your CV, including employment history, education details, skills, and other relevant information.
User-generated content such as photos and documents that you choose to upload to the App.
Communication and correspondence with us, including emails, support inquiries, and feedback.
2.2. Automatically Collected Information:
Technical information about your device, including your device type, operating system, browser type, and IP address.
Usage information, such as the features of the App you interact with, the pages you visit, and your interactions with advertisements.
Information is collected through cookies and similar tracking technologies (please refer to our Cookie Policy for more details).
How We Use Your Information
We may use your personal information for the following purposes:
3.1. Providing Services:
To create and maintain your CV based on the information you provide.
To provide access to the App's features and functionalities.
To communicate with you, respond to your inquiries, and provide customer support.
3.2. Personalization:
To customize your experience on the App and offer tailored content and recommendations.
3.3. Analytics and Improvement:
To analyze user behavior and trends to improve our App's functionality, features, and user experience.
3.4. Marketing and Promotions:
To send you promotional emails and notifications about our products, services, or special offers (you can opt-out at any time).
3.5. Legal Compliance:
To comply with applicable laws, regulations, or legal processes.
To protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property, and that of our users.
How We Share Your Information
We may share your personal information with third parties for the following purposes:
Service providers who help us operate and maintain the App, including hosting analytics, and marketing services.
Business partners and advertisers for marketing and advertising purposes.
Legal authorities or law enforcement agencies when required by law or to protect our legal rights.
Your Choices and Rights
You may have certain rights regarding your personal information, including:
The right to access and review your personal information.
The right to update or correct your personal information.
The right to request the deletion of your personal information.
The right to opt-out of marketing communications.
To exercise these rights, please contact us at
appsresort5@gmail.com.
Security
We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. However, no online platform can be completely secure, so we cannot guarantee the security of your data.
Changes to Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the effective date will be updated.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
Email:
appsresort5@gmail.com.
By using our App, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy. Please review it carefully and check for updates regularly.
